Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:08.49,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥が高鳴る 熱い声に気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:13.87,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,スタートラインは 君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.36,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.92,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.99,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.29,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,素敵だと思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:30.27,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも不安はすぐ側で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:36.16,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,駆け出す思いを 締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.50,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,今を越えて 歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.20,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:47.75,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,初めてを繰り返し 掴み取れ明日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:53.69,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,そうさ 僕たちは無限の夢抱きしめ進むのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:59.46,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝いてる 自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:05.14,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる力に 最大の愛を込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.93,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,思うまま 旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:13.70,tari--OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,新しい 世界の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:08.49,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到胸中澎湃的声音时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:13.87,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起跑线就出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.36,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是一条看不见的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:19.92,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要开始奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.99,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样总比放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:25.29,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:30.27,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安总在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:36.16,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡着自由的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:39.50,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越现在 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.20,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把光明撒向那未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:47.75,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最初的轮回中 找到通往明天的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:53.69,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进中的我们怀有无尽的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:59.46,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信闪耀的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:05.14,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将永不放弃的力量用最大的爱包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.93,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始我们的旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:13.70,tari--OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走向那崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.97,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广播说下午会停的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:14.81,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.16,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「音乐会要穿得整整齐齐去」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:22.27,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是被你妈妈这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:23.77,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.94,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天星期天 食堂不开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:28.68,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:30.60,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:35.47,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:43.99,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:39.52,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大君 今天是一点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.69,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用非得来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.64,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈说想拍照留念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.77,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防水罩真是要对了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.24,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.99,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定别的人根本不来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.36,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别要求太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:00.85,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是 至少来夏也许会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.17,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:07.61,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们… 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.53,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 能别那副样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.51,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就算只有你们一个社团 也要举行白祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.47,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.00,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样下雨也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.14,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定啊 在体育馆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:23.78,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.81,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 新闻部的人叫我去采访
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.64,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经和朋友说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:30.77,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.72,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你告诉他们 我们要上头版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.82,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校报纸又没有什么头版二版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.03,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.13,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.46,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.37,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.74,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到会做到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:24.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 自行车停放场也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.06,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车场也有警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.73,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个高度很轻松就能翻过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是来看的人进不去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.45,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就在这里唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.43,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有雨衣是没问题 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.01,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们太天真了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:44.42,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 喂？ 啊 这样 嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:43.79,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先进去一下吧 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.13,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不砸掉锁链吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:45.84,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.60,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}诶 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:49.06,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:53.75,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浜田说 体育馆也全上了锁 进不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:54.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.95,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.24,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是费事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.84,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 大智
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:08.27,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.44,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 来夏 能爬上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.15,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样没可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.78,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.46,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点东西落在教室里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:28.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.98,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.21,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自来办文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.52,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是合唱团的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.94,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也是羽毛球部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.37,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.45,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个学校的理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.12,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有规定星期天是禁止入内的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.51,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有今天一天请给我们许可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.51,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都准备好了才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.20,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在准备开始之前 你们就应该先申请许可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去申请了校方会批准吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.36,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会商讨的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.59,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有许可我们也会办的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:09.03,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了唱歌而胡来 受到处罚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.33,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是会影响前程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.94,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是威胁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.93,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是教育
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:21.04,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认清自己只是幼稚无力的年轻人这一事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.16,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去开办吧 文化祭 我批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.21,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.45,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是这个学校的校长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭并不需要经过理事长的批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.34,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长也没有直接处罚学生的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.87,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然倒是可以革我的职
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.56,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.92,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为合唱团的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:59.62,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却什么都没做 请原谅这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.07,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:05.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你的教育力度不够 才会发展成这样的事态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么教育
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.34,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明连人心的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:12.94,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和抚慰这份脆弱的歌曲之美妙都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:18.05,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对你而言这里只是一处资产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.16,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于学生却是很重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.33,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聚在一起唱歌而已 唱唱有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.81,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊 难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.17,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了歌曲还有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.79,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.16,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.78,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始不用来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.40,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:49.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找人去坡底下站着 通知来人文化祭取消
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:50.00,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:51.33,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.87,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们连这样的东西都做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.59,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会让我多费那么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.01,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.24,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长先生的解雇手续办完的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭也该结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:16.57,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天音乐科会以声乐部和吹奏乐部为核心充当你们的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.11,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.70,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是合唱和伴奏的曲谱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:24.25,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声乐部和吹奏乐部不久之前就在练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.22,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了这曲子没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.54,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.77,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你动员建起来的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.99,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我担任指挥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.71,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.89,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.58,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管校门还是体育馆 我都没有开放的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.71,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经让停车场的警卫们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:58.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来参加的人都会被引导到那边入场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.33,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 舞台还没……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.25,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.40,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不会有人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.95,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不会来早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.79,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是了吧 白祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.07,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:24.94,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.03,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是第一个到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第一个也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.99,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌请认真一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.62,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧吧 和来夏一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.35,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:39.74,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 来太早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.99,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:55.79,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.18,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的学生已经在校内开始准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:00.20,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:00.73,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:02.05,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.64,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.46,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.72,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是广畑同学去求教导主任的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.32,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要撒这么奇怪的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.52,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广畑同学 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:29.72,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为声乐部没什么目标的话 也会是一盘散沙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.21,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这边是舞台的左首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那钢琴就放这边咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.49,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是乐队演奏席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:40.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.46,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是质量上乘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:45.58,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.01,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩排的机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.18,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和练习时一样的话 我们这边会配合的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.74,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加白祭的宾客请从这里入场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.77,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加白祭请走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 不过 雨停了真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.05,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.82,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式表演的时候不许加入奇怪的即兴发挥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:11.96,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:15.18,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仔细推敲过了 不会破坏剧情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.42,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不许就是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.47,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.37,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.58,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是音乐之国 白滨萨歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:38.65,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开祖国的来夏琪娜踏上旅途的那一刻 故事由此展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.13,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:43.02,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 已经不能再待在这个国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:46.12,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 今后你打算去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:49.49,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要前往遥远的天之岩窟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:51.61,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.65,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺是青蛙小智
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.40,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是青蛙王子 维也纳利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:56.98,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.68,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经过重重磨难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.35,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于走到了今天这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.83,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们却已失去了太多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.74,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人与朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.43,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想与荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.24,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就连最爱的家乡也……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:23.20,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人在黑暗笼罩的世界 看不到未来的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:27.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 只要向着歌声回荡的方向前进就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.22,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我们歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.12,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此作为彼此之间的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.82,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算奇迹不会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅为了暂时的小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.29,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让各自的想念搭上歌声的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.82,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我们还要再上路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:12.89,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湛蓝的天空下 将双手伸展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:20.47,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷茫也好 痛苦也好 都是有过梦想的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:26.40,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的步调前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:34.87,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:45.33,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为骤雨终究会过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:52.48,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白流泪感觉的心 一定是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:14:00.04,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呼唤你 轻拍你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:07.00,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这份旋律 带来了光明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:11.14,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀的瞳孔里映照着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:17.29,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱梦想希望的心 一定永远自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:24.89,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呼唤你 与你一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:31.78,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这份旋律 招来了光明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:38.13,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路再弯曲都已经不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:52.06,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用闪亮的笑容呼唤君之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.64,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲教我骑马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.45,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那匹马非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 杨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.75,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在那乐呵呵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.00,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤吧摔跤吧摔跤吧摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:03.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:05.69,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到保送了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.39,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱羽打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:10.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.34,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出国？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.14,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 国外也有骑术学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.28,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也许还有机会可以成为骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.10,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.02,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.34,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会非常困难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:33.61,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过去了之后也许回日本也能当上骑手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:34.71,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:36.07,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情不愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.35,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校会有考试的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.13,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想尽可能快点去留学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.46,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从语言开始学起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:47.58,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.06,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.57,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这边的学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.01,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算退学但
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.41,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟老师说了以后决定将我做毕业生处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.23,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟学校也有学校的考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.02,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不希望毕业生的人数减少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:04.98,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.03,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.17,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 好突然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.43,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.04,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到我满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.57,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.01,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭着跑回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.21,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.62,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把萨布雷也带去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.65,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.21,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:35.41,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风抚摸着嫩绿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.32,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出国去哪里？ 香港？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:43.24,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远方是那样的澄净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:51.01,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻转动的光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:59.90,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔地看着这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:09.17,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在不见星光的雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:16.13,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看着梦想 未来就在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:24.52,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱吧 无所谓何时 一切随心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:32.06,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的声音传到那夜空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:40.25,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某个地方 如果你听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:44.37,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回忆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:52.50,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些充满兴奋的时日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:19:01.02,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在欢笑中度过的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:46.56,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.52,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是教导主任的乐谱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.81,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是合唱大赛完了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.79,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相签了名交换过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.39,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真昼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.78,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就感觉自己仿佛也拥有了音乐的天分一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:12.11,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我没能和真昼一样走上音乐的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.07,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心 又觉得丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.97,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却始终没能主动放弃它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是我妈妈在说「不要放弃」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.08,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前整理遗物的时候发现了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.72,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她总是一副很高兴的样子唱这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.85,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真昼总是很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.40,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心的就是这个 经常被弄得很焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.27,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.12,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种她天生无所不能一样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:48.11,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想正式进修音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.65,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年大概是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.83,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想去那样的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:56.83,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业之后这方面的事情也能来请教您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.93,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是音乐老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:14.22,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着白色海滨的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:19.75,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上长长的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:25.83,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬息而过的日子与眼前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:31.33,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是永远飞扬的和弦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:35.04,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allegro vivace [活泼的快板]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.86,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:43.49,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.43,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一加一等于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.47,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.30,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的二是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:54.06,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种习惯要先告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.18,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请重拍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.50,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 拍得挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.43,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中就这样？ 没什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.02,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 矮冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.33,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}害羞了害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.96,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱羽 改天我去那边找你玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.63,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:12.44,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 偶尔是羽毛球部的白滨坂合唱团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.40,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上最后一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:16.59,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:21.80,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崭新的风吹拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:29.51,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时欢笑有时哭泣有时放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:35.04,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着敞开自己的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:42.07,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻哼海风的和弦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:22:02.66,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是晴天还是雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:09.26,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你们在身边 我总能露出笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:15.67,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到记忆的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:23.15,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾听记忆中摇晃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:18.03,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.26,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 敦博
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:29.52,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把手递给我 与我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.98,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫本同学 决定加入哪个社团了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:32.70,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:37.24,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不是一个人的空间里 尽情欢乐的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:34.98,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样 一起加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:43.08,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的风吹拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:50.41,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时欢笑有时哭泣有时放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:56.24,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着敞开自己的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:08.16,tari--SUB-m-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻哼记忆里的旋律 奏响乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:18.28,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入八月以后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.13,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒适的放晴期延长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:23.55,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将使全国的天气变得更适于暑假出行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.26,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来 请收听关东地区的天气概况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.07,tari--SUB-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
